it.polimi.se2018.model

Class PlayerMoveParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2018.model.PlayerMoveParameters

  • public class PlayerMoveParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for the parameters required by a toolcard.cardAction() or diceMove() method in order to modify the model according to the player's input. Contains an attribute wpc (the player's board) and an ArrayList of Integer values. The values are sorted in a predefined way, so that in the method cardAction() it's possible to associate each value with the corresponding user input.
